  "commentary": "With SPX spot at 6775 sitting just below the GEX flip at 6776, dealers are in PIN regime and likely selling any push above the flip while providing support on dips toward the 6765 max negative gamma strike. The massive positive gamma wall at 6785 (+33B) creates a strong ceiling where dealers will aggressively sell rallies, while the wall break event suggests we just breached a key level and may see initial momentum before mean reversion kicks in. Key strikes to watch are 6776 flip level for regime changes, 6765 downside support where dealers buy, and 6785 upside resistance where dealers sell hard.\n\nBottom line: expect price to ping-pong between 6765 and 6785 with limited breakout potential.",
